Pain.JunkShield:
Pain.OilSlider:
Pain.WaveBurner:
Pain.WaveBurnerUW:
Pain.Misc:
Pain.Treble:
Pain.FlameSwordSpark:
PLAY H 0 A_SpawnItemEx("BloodHit")
Goto pain+1

Pain.WaterBalloon:
Pain.FlashBomb:
Pain.RemoteMine:
Pain.IceWall:
PLAY H 0 A_SpawnItemEx("BloodHit")
PLAY H 0 A_ScaleVelocity(0.9)
Goto Pain+1
Pain.SpreadDrill:
